# Rain sound; similar to white noise except the so-so darker "splashy" bursts.
Rcos f50 p!{Wsin f10/2 a10^5/2} t60 a1/2

# Thunderous sound, oscillating between rumbly and crackly (rather soft) part;
# amplitude fading in and out works pretty well, but too regular to seem real.
Wsin f-50 f!+50{Rcos r1*2 r!10*2{Wsin f1/10}} a0 a!1{Wsin f3/20} t60
